\pard\plain \fi288\sb240\sl480\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 <$Scr_Ps::0>The caf was buzzing. Today was the day that they called you in and told you the official recommendations of New Kendall Corporation for your future employment \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1  The List. The AI had spoken and today you were to listen to its three magic choices for the rest of your life. Junior had already gotten his. He looked surprised.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93So what did the Wizard of Oz have to say?\u8221\'94 Mik asked. \u8220\'93Anything good?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t know, I\u8217\'92m still trying to figure that out,\u8221\'94 Junior said.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Well, what were your three choices?\u8221\'94 Mik asked. \u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t be shy.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s the thing. They didn\u8217\'92t even give me three,\u8221\'94 he said. \u8220\'93Just one. And I wasn\u8217\'92t expecting it.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93And?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93They want me to study Bahasa.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93What the fuck is that?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s what they speak in Indonesia. They said they need more people who speak their language because they want to expand operations there and I\u8217\'92d be a good candidate.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Why you?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Junior looked embarassed. \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Well, you know\u8230\'85\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93No!\u8217\'92 Mik exclaimed. \u8220\'93Just because you\u8217\'92re Asian?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Junior nodded. \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93And my family came from the Phillipines, not Indonesia. Thirty years ago. I\u8217\'92ve never even been to Asia. I told them that, but you know what they said?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Can\u8217\'92t even imagine.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93\u8217\'92Close enough.\u8217\'92 Can you fucking believe that? They want me to learn the language and then be an interpreter for them.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Here?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93No they want me to learn it here but then move there,\u8221\'94 Junior said. \u8220\'93You know what it felt like? Like they were saying \u8216\'91Go back to where you came from\u8217\'92 only they didn\u8217\'92t even have that right.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93That\u8217\'92s messed up,\u8221\'94 Mik said. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92ve never heard of anything like that. Something must be messed up over there. What are you going to do?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93What can I do?\u8221\'94 Junior said. \u8220\'93You heard what Seanito said. Mess with them and you\u8217\'92ll never be right. Always be working with people who don\u8217\'92t want you.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Maybe. Who knows if Big Sean really has it right. But I could see it\u8217\'92s a big risk. What do you think your folks will say.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93No idea,\u8221\'94 Junior said. \u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m still trying to figure out how to tell them. They wanted me to go for Monetization, just like your folks. All the parents think Monetization is like winning the lottery. I hope they don\u8217\'92t blame me, like I did something wrong.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Or maybe you did something right. Sounds like they think you can handle crises. Like the Alewife bridge.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Oh, fuck, I hadn\u8217\'92t thought of that. You\u8217\'92re right! They must have seen that as a little test \hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1  we didn\u8217\'92t freak out, we didn\u8217\'92t rat them out to Everywhere, we kept our mouths shut even here in New Kendall. \u8216\'91We can trust that kid.\u8217\'92 Now I wish I had said something.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93Then they\u8217\'92d be recommending you for maintenance. Sewer repair specialist, fourth class. So count your blessings, I guess.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8220\'93It still feels like I\u8217\'92ve landed in the shit anyway.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 They picked over their soy chili in silence. Mik felt bad for Junior, which gave way to feeling anxious about his session with The List adviser, which would be right after lunch. }
